NAT – Network Address Translation
=================================

Topology Recap
•	LAN (inside private): 192.168.20.0/24
•	NAT Pool (public IPs): 200.100.50.10 – 200.100.50.20
•	WAN (between R0 & R2): 200.100.50.0/24
•	Server Network (outside): 8.8.8.0/24

Configure Router0 (NAT Router)

      Enable(en)
      configure terminal (conf t)
LAN interface (inside)

•	interface g0/0
•	ip address 192.168.20.1 255.255.255.0
•	ip nat inside
•	no shutdown



WAN interface (outside)
•	interface g0/1
•	ip address 200.100.50.1 255.255.255.0
•	ip nat outside
•	no shutdown

ACL for inside LAN
•	access-list 1 permit 192.168.20.0 0.0.0.255

NAT Pool
•	ip nat pool MYPOOL 200.100.50.10 200.100.50.20 netmask 255.255.255.0

Bind ACL to NAT Pool
•	ip nat inside source list 1 pool MYPOOL

OSPF process ID 45
•	router ospf 45
•	network 192.168.20.0 0.0.0.255 area 0
•	network 200.100.50.0 0.0.0.255 area 0

